    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p><p>Once golden, transfer the <strong>toasted seeds</strong> to a plate and reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 1,
