    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>chicken breast strips</strong> and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until golden and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>cooked chicken</strong></p>",
