    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>shredded kale</strong> to a large pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 2-3 min or until all the kale is tender</p><p>Once cooked, drain and rinse your <strong>cooked kale</strong> under <strong>cold running water </strong>for 5 secs or until slightly cooled</p><p>Shake off any excess water and set the sieve over your pot to drain completely</p>",
